OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1773778273
OL,3,CAfghanistan accuses Pakistan of
OL,4,Cairstrike on hospital that killed more
OL,5,Cthan 400
OL,7,FAfghanistan has accused Pakistan of an
OL,8,Fairstrike on a Kabul hospital that
OL,9,Fkilled at least 400 people and injured
OL,10,Fmore than 250.
OL,12,FThe deadly strike on a drug
OL,13,Frehabilitation hospital in the Afghan
OL,14,Fcapital marked a dramatic escalation
OL,15,Fin a conflict that began last month.
OL,17,FThere have been repeated cross-border
OL,18,Fclashes and airstrikes within
OL,19,FAfghanistan despite international
OL,20,Fpressure to agree a ceasefire.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
