PN,31802
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1773778273
OL,3,CAfghanistan accuses Pakistan of
OL,4,Cairstrike on hospital that killed more
OL,5,Cthan 400
OL,7,FPakistan denied hitting the hospital,
OL,8,Fsaying strikes conducted in eastern
OL,9,FAfghanistan did not hit any civilian
OL,10,Fsites.
OL,12,FThe strikes came hours after Afghan
OL,13,Fofficials said the two sides exchanged
OL,14,Ffire along their common border,
OL,15,Fkilling four people in Afghanistan.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
