OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,319,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1773778273
OL,3,CAfghanistan accuses Pakistan of
OL,4,Cairstrike on hospital that killed more
OL,5,Cthan 400
OL,7,FIn a post on X, Afghanistan's deputy
OL,8,Fgovernment spokesperson Hamdullah
OL,9,FFitrat said the airstrike had hit the
OL,10,Fhospital in Kabul at about 9pm local
OL,11,Ftime, destroying large sections of the
OL,12,F2,000-bed facility. He said the death
OL,13,Ftoll had "so far" reached 400 people,
OL,14,Fwhile about 250 people had been
OL,15,Freported injured.
OL,26,@uD@JOUuD@QO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
