PN,31804
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1773778273
OL,3,CAfghanistan accuses Pakistan of
OL,4,Cairstrike on hospital that killed more
OL,5,Cthan 400
OL,7,FAfghan government spokesperson
OL,8,FZabihullah Mujahid condemned the
OL,9,Fstrike on X, accusing Pakistan of
OL,10,F"targeting hospitals and civilian
OL,11,Fsites to perpetrate horrors." In a
OL,12,Fpost before the death toll rose into
OL,13,Fthe hundreds, he said those killed and
OL,14,Finjured were patients at the hospital.
OL,16,F"We strongly condemn this crime and
OL,17,Fconsider such an act to be against all
OL,18,Faccepted principles and a crime
OL,19,Fagainst humanity," he posted.
OL,26,@rD@AOUsD@]O]xD@AOU{D@RO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/10
