OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1773778273
OL,3,CAfghanistan accuses Pakistan of
OL,4,Cairstrike on hospital that killed more
OL,5,Cthan 400
OL,7,FPakistan's Information Minister
OL,8,FAttaullah Tarar posted on X in the
OL,9,Fearly hours of Tuesday that the
OL,10,FPakistani military had "carried out
OL,11,Fprecision airstrikes" targeting
OL,12,Fmilitary installations in Kabul and
OL,13,Fthe eastern province of Nangarhar. He
OL,14,Fsaid "technical support infrastructure
OL,15,Fand ammunition storage facilities" at
OL,16,Ftwo locations in Kabul were destroyed.
OL,26,@rD@XOUsD@UO]vD@FOUwD@bO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/10
