OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1773778273
OL,3,CAfghanistan accuses Pakistan of
OL,4,Cairstrike on hospital that killed more
OL,5,Cthan 400
OL,7,F"All targeting has been done with
OL,8,Fprecision only at those
OL,9,Finfrastructures which are being used
OL,10,Fby Afghan Taliban regime to support
OL,11,Fits multiple terror proxies," he wrote.
OL,13,FThe strike came hours after the UN
OL,14,FSecurity Council called on
OL,15,FAfghanistan's Taliban rulers to
OL,16,Fimmediately step up efforts to combat
OL,17,Fterrorism.
OL,26,@oD@AOUsD@]O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/10
