PN,31807
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1773778273
OL,3,CAfghanistan accuses Pakistan of
OL,4,Cairstrike on hospital that killed more
OL,5,Cthan 400
OL,7,FThe Security Council resolution,
OL,8,Fadopted unanimously, didn't refer
OL,9,Fspecifically to attacks carried out in
OL,10,FPakistan but condemns "in the
OL,11,Fstrongest terms all terrorist
OL,12,Factivity, including terrorist
OL,13,Fattacks." The resolution also extends
OL,14,Fthe UN political mission in
OL,15,FAfghanistan, UNAMA, for three months.
OL,26,@rD@WOUuD@IO]
