PN,31808
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1773778273
OL,3,CAfghanistan accuses Pakistan of
OL,4,Cairstrike on hospital that killed more
OL,5,Cthan 400
OL,7,FPakistan's government accuses
OL,8,FAfghanistan of providing safe haven to
OL,9,Fthe Pakistani Taliban, which is
OL,10,Fdesignated as a terrorist organisation
OL,11,Fby the United States, as well as to
OL,12,Foutlawed Baloch separatist groups and
OL,13,Fother militants who frequently target
OL,14,FPakistani security forces and
OL,15,Fcivilians across the country. Kabul
OL,16,Fdenies the charge.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
