PN,31809
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1773778273
OL,3,CAfghanistan accuses Pakistan of
OL,4,Cairstrike on hospital that killed more
OL,5,Cthan 400
OL,7,FClashes in October reignited the
OL,8,Fconflict, breaking a ceasefire
OL,9,Fbrokered by Qatar in October and
OL,10,Fleading Pakistan to declare it is in
OL,11,F"open war" with Afghanistan.
OL,13,FThe conflict has alarmed the
OL,14,Finternational community, particularly
OL,15,Fas the area is one where other
OL,16,Fmilitant organisations, including al-
OL,17,FQaida and the Islamic State group,
OL,18,Fstill have a presence and have been
OL,19,Ftrying to resurface.
OL,26,@sD@AOUsD@JO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/10
