PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1773778273
OL,3,CAfghanistan accuses Pakistan of
OL,4,Cairstrike on hospital that killed more
OL,5,Cthan 400
OL,7,FOn Sunday, Tarar said the military has
OL,8,Fkilled 684 Afghan Taliban forces, a
OL,9,Fclaim rejected by Afghanistan, which
OL,10,Fsays casualties are far lower.
OL,11,FAfghanistan's Defence Ministry and
OL,12,Fother officials have said Afghanistan
OL,13,Fhas killed more than 100 Pakistani
OL,14,Fsoldiers.
OL,16,FReporting History sees journalists
OL,17,Fjoin News At Ten anchor Tom Bradby to
OL,18,Frevisit their remarkable on-the-day
OL,19,Freports of defining events of the
OL,20,Fmodern age. Listen to the episodes
OL,21,Fbelow...
